virtu (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian / Ubuntu packaging for Milestone 10 (slice 10.7).
  * Single binary plus shared man page; bundled knowledge base is
    compiled in via include_str! so no runtime data files are needed.
  * Hermetic test suite runs under override_dh_auto_test.

